snippet.title: Cube Escape: The Mill Trailer [Rusty Lake]
snippet.description:
Promo for Cube Escape: Cube Escape: The Mill

Welcome to the Rusty Lake Mill, the residence of Mr. Crow. A familiar guest will arrive soon and it is your task to get that mysterious machine running.

Download now for iOS (Iphone and Ipad):
https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1022292932
Download on Android:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.RustyLake.CubeEscapeTheMill
Or play on web:
http://www.rustylake.com/room-escape-games/cube-escape-the-mill.html

Play more Cube Escape games at RustyLake.com
